showdown.abilities.mummy.changeAbility=%s's Ability became Mummy!
showdown.abilities.myceliummight.name=Сила мицелия
showdown.abilities.myceliummight.desc=This Pokémon's Status moves ignore certain Abilities of other Pokémon, and go last among Pokémon using the same or greater priority moves.
