showdown.moves.gmaxvoltcrash.name=Г-макс Вольт крушение
showdown.moves.gmaxvoltcrash.desc=Power is equal to the base move's Max Move power. If this move is successful, each Pokémon on the opposing side becomes paralyzed, even if they have a substitute.
