showdown.moves.tidyup.name=Уборка
showdown.moves.tidyup.desc=Raises the user's Attack and Speed by 1 stage. Removes subtitutes from all active Pokémon and ends the effects of Spikes, Stealth Rock, Sticky Web, and Toxic Spikes for both sides.
