showdown.moves.whirlwind.name=Вихрь
showdown.moves.whirlwind.desc=The target is forced to switch out and be replaced with a random unfainted ally. Fails if the target is the last unfainted Pokémon in its party, or if the target used Ingrain previously or has the Suction Cups Ability.
